snippet.title: Best VGM 2234 - Alundra 2 - Pirates of Puerto Medusa
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1395 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=62_S0Sl02TM

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation
Alundra 2 (1999)
Pirates of Puerto Medusa
Kohei Tanaka
